<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Confirmation - Dr. Agarwal's Workshop</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .success-box {
      background-color: #e6f7ec;
      border-left: 4px solid #52c41a;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .workshop-details {
      background-color: #f0e6ff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .payment-info {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Payment Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="success-box">
        <h2>Payment Successfully Received!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for completing your payment for Dr. Agarwal's Psychology Workshop.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      
      <p>We're pleased to confirm that your payment for the Psychology Workshop has been successfully processed. Your spot is now fully secured!</p>
      
      <div class="workshop-details">
        <h3>Workshop Details</h3>
        <p><strong>Dates:</strong> {{workshopDetails.dates}}</p>
        <p><strong>Timing:</strong> {{workshopDetails.timing}}</p>
      </div>
      
      <p>We will send you a reminder email with the workshop materials and joining instructions a few days before the event.</p>
      
      <div class="payment-info">
        <p>A copy of your payment receipt is attached for your records.</p>
        
        {{#if paymentScreenshotUrl}}
        <p>Your payment screenshot has been received and verified.</p>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your registration, please contact us as soon as possible.</p>
      
      <p>We look forward to seeing you at the workshop!</p>
      
      <p>Warm regards,<br>
      Dr. Agarwal's Workshop Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Dr. Agarwal's Psychology Workshop. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 